  - channel (enum: email/sms/in-app)
  - enabled (boolean)
  - prefs_json (JSON)

- User
  - id (UUID)
  - name, email, phone
  - verified (boolean)
  - deposits (numeric)

- EventLog (for analytics)
  - id
  - listing_id
